name: Saci - Solo Performance
description:
Saci is a well-known character of the Brazilian mythology.

He has a pipe, a magical red hood and only one leg.

He is always messing around.

Night travelers fear his whistles but he is not evil, just like to joke.

His name has Tupi-Guarani origin.

Saci (Davi Fonseca)
Solo Performance by Davi Fonseca
Sound Engineer - Alexandre Andrés
